 unrest as magmatic or non-magmatic|journal=Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Society A: Mathematical, Physical and Engineering Sciences|date=25 February 2019|volume=377|issue=2139|pages=20180008|doi=10.1098/rsta.2018.0008|pmid=30966934|pmc=6335482}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Feigl4\">Feigl et al. 2018, p.4</ref>\n<ref name=\"Feigl2\">Feigl et al. 2018, p.2</ref>\n<ref name=\"Feigl1\">Feigl et al. 2018, p.1</ref>\n<ref name=\"Andersen68\">Andersen et al. 2018, p.68</ref>\n<ref name=\"Andersen59\">Andersen et al. 2018, p.59</ref>\n<ref name=\"Andersen58\">Andersen et al. 2018, p.58</ref>\n<ref name=\"Sernageomin\">{{cite web|title=Complejo Volc\u00e1nico Laguna del Maule|url=http://www.sernageomin.cl/complejo-volcanico-laguna-del-maule/|website=[[SERNAGEOMIN]]|accessdate=19 February 2018|language=es}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Onemi2017\">{{cite news|title=Se cancela Alerta Temprana Preventiva para la comuna de San Clemente por actividad del complejo volc\u00e1nico Laguna del Maule|url=http://www.onemi.cl/alerta/se-levanta-alerta-amarilla-y-declara-alerta-temprana-preventiva-para-la-comuna-de-san-clemente-por-actividad-volcanica/|accessdate=19 February 2018|agency=[[ONEMI]]|date=13 January 2017}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AndersenSinger2017\">{{cite journal|last1=Andersen|first1=Nathan L.|last2=Singer|first2=Brad S.|last3=Jicha|first3=Brian R.|last4=Beard|first4=Brian L.|last5=Johnson|first5=Clark M.|last6=Licciardi|first6=Joseph M.|title=Pleistocene to Holocene Growth of a Large Upper Crustal Rhyolitic Magma Reservoir beneath the Active Laguna del Maule Volcanic Field, Central Chile|journal=Journal of Petrology|date=1 January 2017|volume=58|issue=1|pages=85\u2013114|doi=10.1093/petrology/egx006|language=en|issn=0022-3530|bibcode=2017JPet...58...85A}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Miller25\">Miller et al. 2017, p.25</ref>\n<ref name=\"Miller16\">Miller et al. 2017, p.16</ref>\n<ref name=\"Miller15\">Miller et al. 2017, p.15</ref>\n<ref name=\"Cardona9\">Cardona et al. 2018, p.9</ref>\n<ref na