.07A}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AndersenSinger2013\">{{Cite journal|last1=Andersen|first1=N.|last2=Singer|first2=B.S.|last3=Jicha|first3=B.R.|last4=Fierstein|first4=J.|last5=Vasquez|first5=J.A.|title=The Development of a Restless Rhyolite Magma Chamber at Laguna del Maule, Chile|journal=AGU Fall Meeting Abstracts|volume=2013|pages=V51C\u20132676|date=December 2013|bibcode=2013AGUFM.V51C2676A}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"MillerWilliams2014\">{{Cite journal|last1=Miller|first1=C.A.|last2=Williams-Jones|first2=G.|last3=Le Mevel|first3=H.|last4=Tikoff|first4=B.|title=Widespread Gravity Changes and CO2 Degassing at Laguna Del Maule, Chile, Accompanying Rapid Uplift|journal=AGU Fall Meeting Abstracts|volume=2014|pages=V41B\u20134811|date=December 2014|bibcode=2014AGUFM.V41B4811M}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"SielfeldCembrano2013\">{{Cite journal|last1=Sielfeld|first1=G.|last2=Cembrano|first2=J.M.|title=Oblique-to-the-orogen fault systems and it causal relationship with volcanism and geothermal activity in Central Southern Chile: Insights on ENE and NW regional lineaments|journal=AGU Fall Meeting Abstracts|volume=2013|pages=T23E\u20132642|date=December 2013|bibcode=2013AGUFM.T23E2642S}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"PenaSancho2013\">{{cite journal|last1=Pe\u00f1a-Monn\u00e9|first1=Jos\u00e9 Luis|last2=Sancho-Marc\u00e9n|first2=Carlos|last3=Dur\u00e1n|first3=V\u00edctor|last4=Mikkan|first4=Ra\u00fal|title=Geoarchaeological reconstruction of the Caverna de las Brujas (Mendoza, Argentina) for the planning of an archaeological intervention|journal=Quaternary International|date=October 2013|volume=308\u2013309|page=268|doi=10.1016/j.quaint.2012.06.025|bibcode=2013QuInt.308..265P}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Dungan2005\">{{cite web|last1=Dungan|first1=D.A.|last2=Langmuir|first2=C.H.|last3=Spikings|first3=R.|last4=Leeman|first4=W.P.|last5=Goldstein|first5=S.|last6=Davidson|first6=J.P.|last7=Costa|first7=F.|last8=Selles|first8=D.|last9=Bachmann|first9=O.|title=Assimilative recycling of the plutonic roots of Andean arc vol