uqu\u00e9n, Argentina)|journal=[[Magallania|Magallania (Punta Arenas)]]|date=2015|volume=43|issue=1|pages=137\u2013163|doi=10.4067/S0718-22442015000100009}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"DavidsonDungan1987\">{{cite journal|last1=Davidson|first1=Jon P.|last2=Dungan|first2=Michael A.|last3=Ferguson|first3=Kurt M.|last4=Colucci|first4=Michael T.|title=Crust-magma interactions and the evolution of arc magmas: The San Pedro\u2013Pellado volcanic complex, southern Chilean Andes|journal=[[Geology (journal)|Geology]]|volume=15|issue=5|page=443|doi=10.1130/0091-7613(1987)15<443:CIATEO>2.0.CO;2|year=1987|bibcode=1987Geo....15..443D}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"HildrethSinger1998\">{{cite journal|last1=Hildreth|first1=Wes|last2=Singer|first2=Brad|last3=Godoy|first3=Estanislao|last4=Munizaga|first4=Francisco|title=The age and constitution of Cerro Campanario, a mafic stratovolcano in the Andes of Central Chile|journal=Revista Geol\u00f3gica de Chile|date=July 1998|volume=25|issue=1|doi=10.4067/S0716-02081998000100002}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"HildrethGrunder1984\">{{cite journal|last1=HILDRETH|first1=WES|last2=GRUNDER|first2=ANITA L.|last3=DRAKE|first3=ROBERT E.|title=The Loma Seca Tuff and the Calabozos caldera: A major ash-flow and caldera complex in the southern Andes of central Chile|journal=Geological Society of America Bulletin|volume=95|issue=1|page=48|doi=10.1130/0016-7606(1984)95<45:TLSTAT>2.0.CO;2|year=1984|bibcode=1984GSAB...95...45H}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"PritchardJay2013\">{{cite journal|last1=Pritchard|first1=M. E.|last2=Jay|first2=J. A.|last3=Aron|first3=F.|last4=Henderson|first4=S. T.|last5=Lara|first5=L. E.|title=Subsidence at southern Andes volcanoes induced by the 2010 Maule, Chile earthquake|journal=Nature Geoscience|date=1 July 2013|volume=6|issue=8|page=634|doi=10.1038/ngeo1855|bibcode=2013NatGe...6..632P}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"RomeufAguirre1995\">{{cite journal|last1=Romeuf|first1=Natalie|last2=Aguirre|first2=Luis|last3=Soler|first3=Pierre|last4=Feraud|first4=Gilbert|last5=Jaillard|